title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight - Texel Airport - version 1.0
description:
In this addon spotlight we are going to look at Texel Airport (EHTX) version 1.0 which has been released a few days ago. This addon has been created by a community member the airport which is popular for parasailing an flying lessons to MSFS 2020. 

If you want to give the airport a try yourself you can download it from the site below: 
https://flightsim.to/file/19107/netherlands-texel-international-airport-ehtx
